Package: synchrosonic
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pipewire-bin
Description: Linux-first LAN audio streaming and casting application
 SynchroSonic captures and streams Linux system audio to receivers over LAN
 while optionally keeping local playback active on the sender.
